Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:34.89,Imouto-OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Nee, kore sae areba ii tte iu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:41.73,Imouto-OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Soko ni wa nai kara gamushara ni ganbatterun da yo ne
