Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:51.68,Imouto-OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Hontou no kanji wa kimi dake no mono da yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.24,Imouto-OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}Itsudatte jibun tte iu
